            <h2>Primefinance Global Business Accounts</h2>
            <p>NovaTrust Bank business accounts are built to meet the everyday financial needs of businesses of all sizes, from sole traders and startups to established companies and large corporations. Our business accounts come with a full suite of features including unlimited transactions, dedicated business debit cards, multi-user access for your team and seamless integration with leading accounting software. Everything is designed to save you time, reduce admin and give you a clear picture of your business finances at all times.</p>
            <p>Managing your business account with NovaTrust Bank is simple and efficient thanks to our powerful online banking platform. You can make and receive payments, set up standing orders and direct debits, manage multiple accounts in one place and generate detailed financial statements all from your secure online dashboard. Our platform is accessible 24 hours a day, 7 days a week from any device, so you always have full control over your business finances whether you are in the office, on the road or working from home.</p>
            <p>At NovaTrust Bank we are committed to supporting businesses at every stage of their journey. When you open a business account with us you gain access to a dedicated business relationship manager who understands your industry and is available Monday to Friday from 8:30am to 5:00pm to provide financial guidance and support whenever you need it. With no monthly maintenance fees for the first 12 months, competitive transaction rates and a fast online account opening process, NovaTrust Bank is the smart banking choice for businesses that mean business.</p>

